# Influencer Recommendation API Testing
# Gunakan dengan VS Code REST Client Extension

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Data Status Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/data-status
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Validate Brief
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/validate-brief
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brief_id": "BRIEF_001",
  "brand_name": "Beauty Brand",
  "industry": "Beauty",
  "influencer_persona": "Beauty enthusiast, authentic reviewer",
  "total_influencer": 3,
  "budget": 50000000.0
}

### 4. Calculate Adaptive Weights
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/adaptive-weights
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "marketing_objective": ["Cognitive", "Affective"],
  "target_goals": ["Awareness", "Brand Perception"],
  "timing_campaign": "2025-03-15",
  "esg_allignment": ["Cruelty-free"],
  "risk_tolerance": "Medium",
  "niche": ["Beauty", "Lifestyle"],
  "location_prior": ["Indonesia"]
}

### 5. Recommend Influencers (Simple)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/recommend-influencers?adaptive_weights=true&include_insights=true
Content-Type: application/json

